tableSettings.header: Undergraduate Students (program type e.g. BMLSc, BSc, summer students, honours theses, co-op, directed studies)

sqlSettings.query:
With filteredTable As (
SELECT * FROM ? WHERE [type] = 'Undergraduate Students (BA/BSc/Co-op/Directed Studies/MD/Summer Student)'),
shortDegreeNotationTable AS (
SELECT 
    *,
    CASE 
        WHEN degree = 'Master of Physical Therapy (MPT)' THEN 'MPT'
        WHEN degree = 'Doctor of Medicine (MD)' THEN 'MD'
        WHEN degree = 'Doctor of Philosophy (PhD)' THEN 'PhD'
        WHEN degree = 'Bachelor of Arts (BA)' THEN 'BA'
        WHEN degree = 'Master of Science (MSc)' THEN 'MSc'
WHEN degree = 'Master of Health Administration (MHA)' then 'MHA'
WHEN degree = 'Bachelor of Medical Laboratory Science (BMLSc)' then 'BMLSc'
when degree = 'Master of Public Health (MPH)' then 'MPH'
when degree = 'Master of Arts (MA)' then 'MA'
when degree = 'Bachelor of Science (BSc)' then 'BSc'
when degree = 'Doctor of Medicine–Doctor of Philosophy (MD-PhD)' then 'MD-PhD'
when degree = 'Master of Occupational Therapy (MOT)' then 'MOT'
when degree = 'Doctor of Medicine–Doctor of Philosophy (MD-PhD)' then 'MD-PhD'
when degree = 'Master of Science–Doctor of Philosophy (MSc-PhD)' then 'MSc-PhD'
        ELSE degree
    END AS degree_short
FROM filteredTable)
SELECT
    degree,
    COUNT(*) AS [total],
    SUM(CASE WHEN DATE_IS_COMPLETE(dates) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS completed,
    SUM(CASE WHEN NOT DATE_IS_COMPLETE(dates) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS in_progress
FROM (
    SELECT
        CASE 
            WHEN degree_short IS NULL OR degree_short = 'undefined' THEN 'No Degree Listed'
            ELSE degree_short
        END AS degree,
        dates
    FROM shortDegreeNotationTable
) AS t
GROUP BY degree
ORDER BY degree;

sqlSettings.query:
SELECT
  *,
  DOLLAR(amount) AS dollarAmount,

  /* agencyCleaned logic */
  (CASE
     WHEN LOWER(TRIM(agency)) = 'rise' THEN ''
     WHEN LOWER(TRIM(agency)) LIKE '%other%' THEN ''
     ELSE agency
   END) AS agencyCleaned,

  /* sponsorCleaned logic */
  (CASE
     WHEN LOWER(TRIM(agency)) = 'rise' THEN sponsor
     WHEN LOWER(TRIM(agency)) LIKE '%other%' THEN agency
     ELSE ''
   END) AS sponsorCleaned
FROM ?
WHERE [type] != 'Salary Support'
  AND [type] != 'All Types Contract'
